documentation.text:
@notice Receives stargate cross-chain calls
 @dev Implements IStargateReceiver interface

typeDescriptions.typeString: function (bytes memory) pure external returns (bytes memory)

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

receiveXChainDepositRequest(uint256,uint.details: Should never ever be actually called.

receiveXChainDistributionRequest(uint256.details: Should never ever be actually called.

receiveXChainRepatriationRequest(uint256.details: Should never ever be actually called.

receiveXChainWithdrawalRequest(uint256,b.details: Should never ever be actually called.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

sendXChainDepositRequest(uint256,uint256.details: Requires appropriate fee to be paid via msg.value (use checkXChainDepositFee() above)

params._destWallet: A valid address on the remote chain that can claim ownership
params._maxMarketMovement: Acceptable degree of slippage on any transaction (e.g. 950 = 5%, 990 = 1% etc.)
params._pid: The pool ID on the remote chain
params._weeksCommitted: Number of weeks to commit to a vault
params._zorroChainId: The Zorro Chain ID (not the LayerZero one)

params._buybackAmountUSD: Amount in USD to buy back
params._revShareAmountUSD: Amount in USD to revshare w/ ZOR single staking vault

sendXChainWithdrawalRequest(uint256,uint.details: Requires value to be submitted to pay for cross chain transaction. Use checkXChainWithdrawalFee() to estimate fees

params._destZorroChainId: The Zorro chain ID of the remote chain to withdraw from
params._gasForDestinationLZReceive: How much additional gas to provide at destination contract
params._maxMarketMovement: Acceptable degree of slippage on any transaction (e.g. 950 = 5%, 990 = 1% etc.)
params._pid: The pool ID on the remote chain
params._trancheId: The ID of the tranche for the given user and pool

params._controller: Bytes representation of smart contract address for cross chain contract

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

receiveXChainDepositRequest(uint256,uint.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

receiveXChainDistributionRequest(uint256.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

receiveXChainRepatriationRequest(uint256.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

receiveXChainWithdrawalRequest(uint256,b.notice: Dummy func to allow .selector call above and guarantee typesafety for abi calls.

sendXChainDepositRequest(uint256,uint256.notice: Prepares and sends a cross chain deposit request. Takes care of necessary financial ops (transfer/locking USD)

sendXChainDistributeEarningsRequest(uint.notice: Sends a request back to the home chain to distribute earnings

sendXChainWithdrawalRequest(uint256,uint.notice: Prepares and sends a cross chain withdrwal request.

setControllerContract(uint256,bytes).notice: Setter: Controller contract for each chain

setStargateDestPoolIds(uint256,uint16).notice: Setter: Stargate dest pool IDs for USD asset
